{"type": "article", "id": 29628, "title": "桌上风扇", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-14T23:02:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714181005Rb9DtjAuvK3aqkl6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>韩国设计师 Kwanjun Ryu 最近将可调节的折臂同小风扇结合，设计一款名为 Branch 的桌上小风扇。它的造型很容易使人联想到动画工作室皮克斯的那个“看板灯” Luxo，看上去简洁又迷你。归功于折臂和能够随意旋转的风扇头，你可以随心所欲地控制风扇把凉爽的风送往需要的地方，有着极高的灵活度。美中不足的是它目前还处于原型阶段，尚未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714181034Whji3xvbweLlQIOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714181022ZirzM84Dwdph3YvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.427619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714181022f6T1l7dLwqEYKMnZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.544762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714181022cF91EKyVkTRMeAWw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.586667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}